name: HighFive
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: high five
des:
This feature helps you to share your thoughts with alexa and you can celebrate your moment by asking High five.

Just wake her by saying

Alexa, Open High Five.

Then she will start celebrating with you.

If you wish to share your happy moments, you can say the following 
* Yes, followed by the happy moments you wish to share.

If you didn't answer anything it will ask you whether you want to celebrate it again or not, if you wish to celebrate you can say any one of the following
* Give Me Five.
* Up High.
* Low Five.
* Slapping five.
* Slap hands.
 
If you don't wish to continue, you can say the following
* No
* That's Fine.
* It's Alright
* Leave.

Do try it and post your comments. Whether you feel good or bad, just post both positive and negative comments so that I will make it more better in future.
